caption:
#AcneTreatment can seem overwhelming, but here is a basic primer. Ingredients to look for are salicylic acid, adapalene, and benzoyl peroxide. There's also azelaic acid, sulfur, niacinamide, glycolic acid, succinic acid, and others. But the first three are the main work horse ingredients. If these don't work, then I would see your trusty board-certified derm for other options. 

@CeraVe @La Roche-Posay @LaRochePosayUS @@differinus @PanOxyl 

#acnetreatment #pimples #acne #acnetips #skincareroutine #salicylicacid #adapalene #retinol #benzoylperoxide #panoxyl #acnescar #acneregimen

acne isn’t one-size-fits-all and neither is your routine! it’s less about using everything, and more about using the right thing for the breakout you actually have.

even with the perfect routine, breakouts sometimes still happen. remember to stay consistent regardless, and above all, give yourself a little grace. your skin will tell you what it needs - once you know how to read it 💓

