caption:
Niacinamide is an ingredient loved by dermatologists for having multiple skin benefits. 

Niacinamide can help with hyperpigmentation and redness, restore and repair your skin barrier, and it's an antioxidant with anti-aging benefits like preventing fine lines and wrinkles. 

